section.para:
GINsim is a Java application and should thus run on any system offering a Java virtual machine (version 1.4 or later). If Java is not already installed on your computer, it can be downloaded:
from sun Java page for Windows, Solaris and Linux (i386 and AMD64),
from apple Java page for Mac OS X users,
from IBM Java page for some other systems (AIX, linux-PPC).

